Feature: Inviting founding members
  In order to have the necessary number of members and directors
  As a founder
  I want to invite people to join as founding members of my new co-op

  Scenario: Founder invites new founding members
    Given I am the founder of a new co-op
    When I go to the Members page
    And I enter a new founding member's details
    And I press "Send invitation"
    Then I should see the new founding member in the list of invited members
    And the new founding member should receive an invitation email
